latestIgtvVideos.title: Simple Day time skincare routine 😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Beat your Monday blues with some self pampering!!

Here's a very simple/minimal skincare routine for all the Oily skin beauties out there 🤗
On @akshaya_shekar 's simple routine :

1. @cetaphilus - Cleanser
2. @vilvah_ - Chocolate Face mask
3. @aromamagicnepal - Toner
4. @lush - Lip scrub
5. @lush - Lip balm
6. @clinique_in - Moisture surge
7. Sunscreen that her dermatologist recommended ( you can use good ones available from drugstore) But please don't skip this step 🤗

And of course, mug full of water ☺️

Favourites from Appu’s Green room 😍
We highly entertain such enthusiastic bridesmaids in to the bride’s room and Suchi @maragadhavalliakamaggi was one such bundle of energy ✨
I always try to be around for the first few pictures that the brides get to take with the pro’s just to ensure they don’t feel conscious/awkward but when there are friends like Suchi around I’m sure no one is going to feel anything but only more re assured that they look oh just so beautiful 🫶
